{"tid":2322378,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港電台：12港人案有家屬接來電　要求代被捕人承認本港控罪","createTime":"2020-12-12T09:34:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T13:01:10.000Z","uid":290404,"like":6,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"be0d0fe72a96e992ec652cba6b29b871b4410e5b","tid":2322378,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:34:51.000Z","msg":"港台又乘機侮辱十二義士，將佢地講成「12名涉嫌觸犯內地偷越邊境罪的港人」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564964-20201212.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564964-20201212.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcrO6ciNacqKxYXGqE8pVUEM%3D&h=b1bbe55d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564964-20201212.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=183ead41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564964-20201212.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>12名涉嫌觸犯內地偷越邊境罪的港人</strong>，目前仍被羈押。有家屬指接獲官派律師來電，對方拒絕透露姓名及證明律師資格，<strong>但要求家屬代被捕人承認在本港的控罪。</strong><br />\n<br />\n被拘留人士李子賢的父親表示，早前接獲新一封家書，內容提到無法收到家人回信，同時要求家人代他承認在本港牽涉的控罪。李子賢的父親又指，自稱代表李子賢的官派律師曾經與他聯絡，提出同樣要求，但對方拒絕透露姓名及律師證明。家屬指多番經入境處及駐粵辦去信李子賢，質疑特區政府未有真正協助家屬轉交信件。<br />\n<br />\n而另一名被拘捕的黃偉然，家屬說，官派律師多番查詢黃偉然在本港牽涉的控罪詳情，但對方同樣拒絕證實律師身份，又表示黃偉然會處理律師費的事宜，家屬指黃偉然身無分文，質疑官派律師的說法不可信。<br />\n<br />\n另一名被拘留的鄧棨然，家人說，接獲中國銀行通知，要以「商業行政理由」取消鄧棨然的個人戶口，需要由鄧棨然本人才可領回戶口內的款項。<br />\n<br />\n12名港人的家屬要求，盡快與保安局局長及政務司司長會面，亦要求內地當局盡快公布審訊日期，讓家屬預留足夠時間在內地隔離檢疫及聽審。"},{"pid":"19d8396fdfdfd28a5d7679417e56e43dda8a602d","tid":2322378,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"989463b7bbed375cd9d8f9f75565e8958149416a","tid":2322378,"uid":43062,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:36:43.000Z","msg":"忽撚咗呀關港台咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有碟話碟陳述事實"},{"pid":"2ccbe91e25194f5f83c8b6c57346fbd7896fe91c","tid":2322378,"uid":301666,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:37:25.000Z","msg":"可以代承認控罪<br />\n但係唔可以代請律師 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb737644f7109fdf067b9cc162addb42bd97646","tid":2322378,"uid":2676,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:37:52.000Z","msg":"樓主智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd4649da58bcd699a8c18ea3ee1a1f500bf8783","tid":2322378,"uid":100337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"989463b7bbed375cd9d8f9f75565e8958149416a","tid":2322378,"uid":43062,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:36:43.000Z","msg":"忽撚咗呀關港台咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有碟話碟陳述事實"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:38:06.000Z","msg":"起佢底啦"},{"pid":"451db1d610e97194718a657cb5a763bba6049a29","tid":2322378,"uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"989463b7bbed375cd9d8f9f75565e8958149416a",